# <type>(<scope>): <imperative summary — max ~72 chars>
#
# Types: feat | fix | content | refactor | chore | deps | ci
# Scopes: lovell-canyon | seo | realscout | engagement | pages | ci | git
#
# Body (optional): why this change, not what line changed.
# Footer (optional): Fixes #123 | BREAKING CHANGE: ...
#
# --- COMMIT CHECKLIST ---
# [ ] One logical change only (atomic)
# [ ] pnpm type-check && pnpm lint pass
# [ ] No .env, secrets, or .vercel staged
# [ ] SEO/NAP correct for lovellcanyon.com if touching pages
